{"id":3201,"date":"2023-01-27T17:25:03","date_gmt":"2023-01-27T16:25:03","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/?page_id=3201"},"modified":"2023-02-01T13:04:29","modified_gmt":"2023-02-01T12:04:29","slug":"general-info","status":"publish","type":"page","link":"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/general-info\/","title":{"rendered":"General Info"},"content":{"rendered":"<div id=\"modal-ready\">\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><img decoding=\"async\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" src=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/2nd-conference-Twitter-1600-\u00d7-900-px-3-1024x576.png\" alt=\"Improving Discovery and Collaboration in Open Science\" class=\"wp-image-2812\" srcset=\"https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/2nd-conference-Twitter-1600-\u00d7-900-px-3-1024x576.png 1024w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/2nd-conference-Twitter-1600-\u00d7-900-px-3-300x169.png 300w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/2nd-conference-Twitter-1600-\u00d7-900-px-3-768x432.png 768w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/2nd-conference-Twitter-1600-\u00d7-900-px-3-1536x864.png 1536w, https:\/\/project.gotriple.eu\/wp-content\/uploads\/2022\/11\/2nd-conference-Twitter-1600-\u00d7-900-px-3.png 1600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" \/><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The final TRIPLE Conference will be a <strong>hybrid event<\/strong>. Presenters are strongly encouraged to be present in person.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>While the registration for on-site attendance is closed,&nbsp;<strong>registration<\/strong>&nbsp;for&nbsp;<strong>online participation<\/strong>&nbsp;is available for everyone. Once you have submitted your registration, you will get a confirmation email. The Zoom link needed for online attendance will be sent around one day before the event.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<p>Have a look at the programme here:&nbsp;<a href=\"https:\/\/project